reviewText: Excellent.  Not an issue but the photograph and description are incorrect.  It is actually the Best of the Two Ronnies Part 2.

The picture on this page shows The Two Ronnies Series 3, which is a two-disc set, but the description says "1 disc". Besides, The Two Ronnies Series 3 already has a separate page. What is this page really about? How can I know what I'd be buying?
